name: Sleepycryptobee's Amegilla Cingulata
description:
This fantastic blue banded bee is an Australian native, and my wife's favourite bee. Thanks for coming on my podcast and making this artwork for me.
Thanks to @sleepycryptobee for producing this artwork. One third of the profits will go towards saving Australian wildlife. 
This piece was produced for the NFT Neighbourhood podcast and is the second  in the series.
